Dia. 01 Another Mistake
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par After White's hane, Black's block at 1 is another mistake.
\par White plays the hane at 2, following the proverb which says "\cf1\b there is death in the hane\cf0\b0 ".
\par
\par After Black plays the tiger's mouth move at 3 White plays the center of the five space shape and captures Black very easily.
\par
\par
\par }
