Dia. 02 White 2, Severe
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Expanding the living space with 1 is a greedy move.
\par White's placement at 2 is severe and then Black can't live anymore.
\par
\par If White plays at A instead of 2, Black lives 2 which was the \cf1\b opponent's vital point \cf0\b0 as well.
\par
\par }
