Dia. 04 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black 1 is the vital point for living.
\par There is another proverb which fits very well to this situation "\cf1\b The vital point is the center of the symmetrical shape\cf0\b0 ".
\par
\par After White's placement at 2, Black lives with 3.
\par The sequence up to 7 proves Black's life.
\par
\par }
